      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been consistently maintained by its previous owner. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a reliable driving experience for its next owner. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, the interior remains clean and the mechanical systems are in great working order. This is a solid, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road.",
